structures

Class Vector2d

  • java.lang.Object
    • structures.Vector2d

  • public class Vector2d
extends java.lang.Object
    Representation of a two dimensional mathematical vector. Supports typical operations on vectors in an immutable fashion.
  • Note that the angle of a vector is defined as being measured in the counter-clockwise direction on the x-axis.
  • Angles are always stored in radians.
Author:
Sean Lewis
